Contents
--
1. ODS export configs moved to import_export_definitions table
2. Activate value search for customfields
3. Email system accounts


--------------------------------------------------------------
1. ODS export configs moved to import_export_definitions table

You need to transfer your custom definitions (formerly saved in config.inc.php) 
into xml format and save them in the import_export_definitions table. You can look 
at the default definitions to see how that is done.


--------------------------------------------------------------
2. Activate value search for customfields

To activate the value search function (and turn the custom field input fields into 
comboboxes) you need to set the value_search field in the custom field config table 
to 1.

sql example:
 update tine20_customfield_config set value_search=1 where type='textfield';

--------------------------------------------------------------
3. Email system accounts
 
 If you want to use system email accounts (you define host/port/... and normal tine
 user credentials are used to connect to the mailserver) for all users you can force 
 the preference 'useSystemAccount' (has been renamed from 'userEmailAccount'). Users 
 with the 'MANAGE_ACCOUNTS' right can change some of the account values (signature, 
 name, ...). 
 